NAME
	lich <message>

DESCRIPTION
	Send a message to the liege-follower channel. Everyone serving
	the same lord/lady as well as the lord/lady him/hewrself will
	hear the message.

	Without arguments show who are listening to the channel.

	"lichoff" set your channel to "off-state", no new messages will
	come thorugh.

	"lichon" sets your channel to "on-state", all messages sent by
	liege/followers will come thorugh.

SEE ALSO
	liege
